parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the fuel tank can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents.
symptoms: Strong gasoline odor
fuel leaks from the tank
corrosion of the metal ring bonded to the tank
rusting of the metal lock ring that holds the fuel pump in place.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel line can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents.
symptoms: Smell of gasoline
fuel spraying from the plastic fuel line
pinhole leaks in the fuel line
fuel leaks from the fuel pump module.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents.
symptoms: Fuel smell when the tank is full
fuel and water leaks
fuel injector failure
fuel pump module not properly secured in the tank.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Traction Control and Anti-Lock Brake System (ABS) Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the traction control and ABS systems can lead to loss of vehicle control, increased stopping distances, and accidents.
symptoms: Traction control light illuminated
ABS light not illuminated despite malfunction
wheel lock-up
steering problems
brake pedal drops to the floorboard
brake fluid pouring from brake line
premature brake wear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can lead to loss of vehicle control, increased stopping distances, and accidents.
symptoms: Brake pedal drops to the floorboard
brake fluid pouring from brake line
premature brake wear
brake pads need to be replaced frequently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake module can lead to loss of vehicle control, increased stopping distances, and accidents.
symptoms: Brake module malfunction
repeated brake repairs
vehicle unreliability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt Failure - Front Driver Side
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front driver side seat belt can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to connect
the seat belt buckle will not latch
the seat belt is unable to be fastened.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt Failure - Rear Passenger Side
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear passenger side seat belt can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to retract
the seat belt does not snug up after being fastened
excessive slack in the seat belt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can increase the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident, as the occupant may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: The retractor spring becomes disengaged
the retainer separates from the rear seat shoulder belt retractor
the spring jumps out of its housing due to heat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn can lead to a lack of audible warning in emergency situations, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The horn fails to sound
the horn sounds intermittently
or the horn sounds weakly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter can leave the driver stranded, unable to start the vehicle, which can be a safety concern in certain situations.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
the starter motor makes a clicking sound but the engine does not turn over
the starter motor does not function at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning service engine soon light can lead to ignored or undiagnosed engine problems, potentially causing engine damage, decreased performance, and decreased fuel efficiency.
symptoms: The service engine soon light turns on and off intermittently
the light remains on constantly
or the light fails to turn on despite engine problems.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the anti-theft system can lead to unauthorized vehicle access, theft, or damage.
symptoms: The anti-theft system fails to arm or disarm
the system triggers false alarms
or the system fails to respond to attempted theft.
